strings.Value: "We should be doubly watchful, if we're to rest in so dangerous a place."
"It's not the safest place to set camp. Keep your weapons close and your eyes open."
"If you care so much about our safety, wouldn't it be better if you stopped talking? Who knows what attention you're attracting?"
"We should choose better places for camp from now on."
"A bad place for camp is where pine cones sting your butt when you sit. But a dangerous place surrounded by enemies â€” that's a good one!"
"Whoa! Well, if the general herself is worried, then there's sure to be trouble, ha, ha."
